d municipalities each portfolio invests only in its specific asset class within the trusts explicit investment guidelines this ensures that the saratoga portfolios always work handinhand with your specific asset allocation investors should note that in other portfolios the portfolio manager may not be required to invest in a manner that is consistent with investors asset allocation goals and in fact may counter the investors asset allocation strategy by imposing a different or contrary allocation within the portfolio to contact saratoga call      saratoga capital management  stewart ave suite  garden city ny  commercial real estate  management  insurance  contact us investment managers  stock brokerage  interactive research contact saperston asset management inc at websaperstoncom if you experience any problems with this web page or have any questions or comments regarding it please email the webmaster at websaperstoncom jfocx quote  saratoga advantage trust  james alpha family office portfolio fund  bloomberg markets error could not add to watchlist x  watchlist saratoga advantage trust  james alpha family office portfolio jfocxus nasdaq gm usd   as of  am edt  fund type openend fund wk range    before its here its on the bloomberg terminal learn more previous close  wk range    fund type openend fund objective dynamic allocation asset class focus mixed allocation geographic focus us nav on   total assets k usd on   inception date  last dividend on   dividend indicated gross yield  fund managers kevin r greene  michael j montague mike front load fee  back load fee  redemption fee  b fee  current mgmt fee  expense ratio  profile james alpha family office portfolio is an openend fund incorporated in the usa the fund seeks total return through capital appreciation andor income the fund utilizes asset allocation data of multiple family offices to construct a diversified portfolio across a broad range of assets classes and investment strategies address the saratoga adva